<topic id="view-status-information">
  <title>Viewing Status Information</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Status information</indexterm>
        <indexterm product="author developer editor">Information view</indexterm>
        <indexterm product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Console view</indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_dnv_bgk_54b">Status information generated by operations such as <i>schema
      detection</i>, <i>manual validation</i>, <i>automatic validation</i>, and
        <i>transformations</i> are fed into the <uicontrol product="author developer editor json"
        >Information</uicontrol>
      <uicontrol product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse">Console</uicontrol> view,
      allowing you to monitor how the operation is being executed<ph
        product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"> (the <xref
          href="preferences-view.dita#preferences-view/enable-oxygen-consoles"><uicontrol>Enable
            Oxygen consoles</uicontrol> option</xref> must be selected in the <xref
          href="preferences-view.dita#preferences-view"><uicontrol>View</uicontrol> preferences
          page</xref>)</ph>. </p>
    <p id="p_env_bgk_54b">
      <fig product="author developer editor json" id="fig_fnv_bgk_54b">
        <title>Information view messages</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_information_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_gnv_bgk_54b">
      <fig product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse" id="fig_hnv_bgk_54b">
        <title>Console View Messages</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_console_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_inv_bgk_54b">Messages contain a timestamp, the name of the thread that generated it,
      and the actual status information. The number of displayed messages can be controlled with the
        <ph product="author developer editor json"><xref
          href="preferences-view.dita#preferences-view/max-number-lines"><uicontrol>Maximum number
            of lines</uicontrol> option</xref> in the <uicontrol>Views</uicontrol></ph><xref
        href="preferences-view.dita#preferences-view/limit-console-output"
        product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"><uicontrol>Limit console
          output</uicontrol> option in the <uicontrol>View</uicontrol></xref> preference page. </p>
    <p id="p_jnv_bgk_54b">To make the view visible, select <menucascade
        product="author developer editor json">
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Information</uicontrol>
      </menucascade><menucascade product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Console</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
  </body>
</topic>